sentences: Numerous Parties supported the Protocol's entry into force by Rio+10 in 2002 including, inter alia: BULGARIA, CARICOM, the EU, FRANCE, GERMANY, HAITI, IRELAND, ITALY, JAPAN, SPAIN, SWEDEN, and the UK.
The EU said more ambitious emissions reduction commitments than those agreed to at Kyoto were needed.
enb_long_title: Fifth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
